<h2 id="50">4. Invoice document</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can create invoices manually or generate them with an <a href="/en/automation/event-procedures#events-documents">event procedure</a>. Either way, it is important to set up a <a href="/en/orders/order-documents#300">document template</a> first. Find more information about invoice documents in the manual section <a href="/en/orders/order-documents/generating-invoices">Invoices</a>.</p>
